HEADWORD: Evil-favored
<hw>E"vil-fa`vored</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having a bad
countenance or appearance; ill-favored; blemished; deformed.</def>
<rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj></p>

<p> -- <wordforms><wf>E"vil-fa`vored*ness</wf>,
